### Custom Cell Size\par
\par
<ComponentPreview\par
  styleName="radix-nova"\par
  name="calendar-custom-days"\par
  title="Custom Cell Size"\par
  description="A calendar with custom cell size that's responsive."\par
  className="**:[.preview]:h-[560px]"\par
/>\par
\par
You can customize the size of calendar cells using the `--cell-size` CSS variable. You can also make it responsive by using breakpoint-specific values:\par
\par
```tsx showLineNumbers\par
<Calendar\par
  mode="single"\par
  selected=\{date\}\par
  onSelect=\{setDate\}\par
  className="rounded-lg border [--cell-size:--spacing(11)] md:[--cell-size:--spacing(12)]"\par
/>\par
```\par
\par
Or use fixed values:\par
\par
```tsx showLineNumbers\par
<Calendar\par
  mode="single"\par
  selected=\{date\}\par
  onSelect=\{setDate\}\par
  className="rounded-lg border [--cell-size:2.75rem] md:[--cell-size:3rem]"\par
/>\par
```\par
