## RTL\par
\par
To enable RTL support in shadcn/ui, see the [RTL configuration guide](/docs/rtl).\par
\par
See also the [Hijri Guide](#persian--hijri--jalali-calendar) for enabling the Persian / Hijri / Jalali calendar.\par
\par
<ComponentPreview\par
  styleName="radix-nova"\par
  name="calendar-rtl"\par
  direction="rtl"\par
  previewClassName="h-96"\par
/>\par
\par
When using RTL, import the locale from `react-day-picker/locale` and pass both the `locale` and `dir` props to the Calendar component:\par
\par
```tsx showLineNumbers\par
import \{ arSA \} from "react-day-picker/locale"\par
\par
;<Calendar\par
  mode="single"\par
  selected=\{date\}\par
  onSelect=\{setDate\}\par
  locale=\{arSA\}\par
  dir="rtl"\par
/>\par
```\par
\par
